text:
Specifically asked for fried chicken not to be chopped and served at full piece, reason being sometimes I know when it's chopped they might not give the whole piece. As you can see, all I had was chicken bones with pathetic amount of meats attached to the bones, the maggi goreng was also too salty, I just couldn't finish it (wouldn't wanna get kidney stones).

And have I mentioned? This plate of "things" cost $7.50?!

The prata quite tasty actually but the chicken mutabak not to our liking. I think for hygiene wise a lot to improve. I saw staff after handling cash use the same hand without glove to handle prata preparation. This standard cannot be acceptable.
Ordered food via Grab. Everything was tasteless. No salt. No spice.
The thosai is done well. The sauces were too salty for my liking
I was nicely surprised by plain thosai with curry sauce! It was amazingly crispy!  Both me and my daughter enjoyed it!
